# Test Lunchio
AngularJs + openweathermap API

### Get Started
1 `git clone https://github.com/akram1rekik/testLunchio.git` 

2 `cd testLunchio`

3 `npm install`

4 `cd app/`

5 `bower install`

6 `http-server`

##### Go to `http://0.0.0.0:8080`
